short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Horsepower is so last year. Measure power in duckpower. This plugin will replace horsepower with vital duckpower measurements.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Horsepower is so last year. Measure power in duckpower. This Chrome extension replaces the word "horsepower" and "duckpower", and even recomputes horsepower figures in duckpower at a ratio of 1 horsepower : 48 duckpower (as supported by
https://www.reddit.com/r/theydidthemath/comments/4woih7/request_how_much_duckpower_is_1_horsepower/). Don't be stuck with last year's power units.
